{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01JTzA8ZJqihhGA1A1p8D1N1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_014La1jVxuPsPXaodepMTtNT","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Minestrone.generated.22.txt","content":"Autumn | Soups | Vegetables\nSERVES 6-8\n\nMinestrone\n\nA hearty Italian vegetable and pasta soup, packed with seasonal vegetables and white beans.\n\nIngredients:\n3 tablespoons olive oil\n1 large onion, diced\n3 cloves garlic, minced\n2 medium carrots, sliced\n2 celery stalks, sliced\n200g zucchini, diced\n200g green beans, chopped\n1 medium potato, diced\n1 red bell pepper, diced\n400g canned tomatoes, crushed\n1 liter vegetable stock\n2 cans (400g each) white beans, drained\n100g small pasta (ditalini or orzo)\n2 bay leaves\n1 teaspoon dried oregano\n½ teaspoon dried thyme\nSalt and pepper to taste\nFresh basil for garnish\nParmesan cheese for serving\n\nMethod:\nHeat olive oil in large pot over medium heat. Sauté onion and garlic until fragrant, about\n3 minutes. Add carrots and celery, cook for 5 minutes. Stir in zucchini, green beans, potato,\nand bell pepper. Cook for another 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.\n\nAdd crushed tomatoes, stock, white beans, pasta, bay leaves, oregano, and thyme. Bring to boil,\nthen reduce heat and simmer for 25-30 minutes until vegetables are tender and pasta is cooked.\n\nSeason generously with salt and freshly ground black pepper. Remove bay leaves. Serve hot,\ngarnished with fresh basil and grated Parmesan cheese. This soup tastes even better the next day.\n\nServes: 6-8\nPreparation: 15 minutes\nCooking: 40 minutes\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":75757,"cache_read_input_tokens":15568,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":75757},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a4939b60-f5d7-4572-ab91-3aec02accfdd","uuid":"c8abd863-d287-459f-a9ef-0b80b7ae02d6"}
