{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01JTzA8ZJqihhGA1A1p8D1N1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01JntM1eV71Zb3SQAuZCvySn","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Baked Tomato Risotto with Basil.generated.22.txt","content":"BAKED TOMATO\nRISOTTO WITH\nBASIL\n\nA modern twist on traditional risotto, baked in the oven for even cooking and enriched\nwith fresh tomatoes and basil.\n\nIngredients:\n300g arborio rice\n600ml hot vegetable stock\n400g canned tomatoes, crushed\n1 medium onion, finely diced\n4 cloves garlic, minced\n100ml dry white wine\n1 tablespoon olive oil\n50g butter\n50g parmesan cheese, grated\n1 tablespoon tomato paste\nLarge handful fresh basil, roughly torn\nSalt and pepper to taste\nExtra basil leaves for garnish\n\nMethod:\nPreheat oven to 190°C. Heat olive oil in large oven-safe pan over medium heat. Sauté onion\nand garlic until translucent, about 3 minutes. Add rice and stir constantly for 2 minutes.\n\nPour in white wine and stir until absorbed. Add tomato paste and crushed tomatoes, stir well.\nPour hot stock over rice, season with salt and pepper. Stir once more, then transfer to oven.\n\nBake covered for 25-30 minutes until rice is tender and liquid is absorbed. Remove from oven,\nstir in butter, parmesan, and fresh basil. Adjust seasoning. Cover and let rest for 2 minutes.\n\nServe immediately, topped with extra fresh basil leaves and additional parmesan cheese.\n\nServes: 4\nPreparation: 10 minutes\nCooking: 35 minutes\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":75757,"cache_read_input_tokens":15568,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":75757},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a4939b60-f5d7-4572-ab91-3aec02accfdd","uuid":"4a7dcd15-b4da-4204-abf8-a673da41bc50"}
